title: Could You Drive an F1 Car?
How Red Bull Uses Tech to Dominate F1
description:
Seeing the Red Bull Racing F1 factory in person, chatting with Max Verstappen, Sergio Perez and Christian Horner along with seeing the insane drone Dutch Drone Gods have built to chase a Formula One car at over 200 MPH is one of the wildest experiences of my life.

Thank you to @MykeHurley for all the helping shooting this video! You can check out our podcast at https://www.relay.fm/backmarkers
